creator: Extend Enterprises
descriptionHtml:
Extend is the most convenient and secure way to send and request access to a credit card.

When employees, contractors, or interviewees need to pay for business purchases such as office supplies, online subscriptions and business travel, Extend provides them with a controlled access to the business credit card. Extend removes the painful reimbursement process, risky card number sharing, and time-consuming act of making purchases for someone else.

Just send or request access to your business’ credit card today to get the full benefits of Extend.
descriptionShort: Send and request access to a credit card.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Getting our ducks in a row for some big new things.

title: Extend

creator: Extend Enterprises
descriptionHtml:
Extend is a modern way for businesses to make and manage payments with their existing corporate cards. In this easy-to-use app, you can instantly create and send secure virtual cards to anyone in your network, improve oversight of spending, and automate reconciliation. Extend has partnered with a number of major card networks and banks to bring you a trusted platform that makes better use of the corporate card that’s already in your wallet and signing up is as easy as creating an Extend login and registering a qualified credit card. It’s absolutely free for businesses with no commitment.

Key features:

- Instantly create and send virtual cards from an existing corporate card
- Recipients can request a virtual card from an active account holder
- Set spending limits, active dates, and more
- Create different cards for different expenses for better expense management
- Assign reference codes and upload attachments for better expense management
- Get real-time updates on spending activity and know who’s spending what and where
- Streamline expense processes and automate reconciliation
- Capture more spend on your company card and earn more rewards
descriptionShort: Create, send, request, and manage virtual cards with your business credit card.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
App redesign includes:
- New, adaptive home screen summarizing your various activity
- New menu bar with new labels, “Send” and “Spend” become “Your cards” and “Accounts”
- Select the different types of virtual cards you can create in the “Create” and “Request” process
- New Virtual Card detail presents the most vital information
- New search options across the app to help you navigate more quickly
- New tooltips, educational tidbits, and reactive alerts

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: We've added a new People section where you can view all of your contacts. You can now add contacts as well as view details for individual people. The "Add People" button replaces the "Invite" button.

title: Extend

creator: Extend Enterprises
descriptionHtml:
Extend is a modern way for businesses to make and manage payments with their existing corporate cards. In this easy-to-use app, you can instantly create and send secure virtual cards to anyone in your network, improve oversight of spending, and automate reconciliation. Extend has partnered with a number of major card networks and banks to bring you a trusted platform that makes better use of the corporate card that’s already in your wallet and signing up is as easy as creating an Extend login and registering a qualified credit card. It’s absolutely free for businesses with no commitment.

Key features:

- Instantly create and send virtual cards from an existing corporate card
- Recipients can request a virtual card from an active account holder
- Set spending limits, active dates, and more
- Create different cards for different expenses for better expense management
- Assign reference codes and upload attachments for better expense management
- Get real-time updates on spending activity and know who’s spending what and where
- Streamline expense processes and automate reconciliation
- Capture more spend on your company card and earn more rewards
descriptionShort: Create, send, request, and manage virtual cards with your business credit card.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: We've added the ability to set up organizations. If you need admin privileges for company credit cards, you can set up your org on the homepage or when you first sign up.

Extend has partnered with a number of major card networks and banks to bring you a trusted platform that makes better use of the corporate card that’s already in your wallet and signing up is as easy as creating an Extend login and registering a qualified credit card. It’s absolutely free for businesses with no commitment.

Key features:

- Instantly create and send virtual cards from an existing corporate card
- Recipients can request a virtual card from an active account holder
- Set spending limits, active dates, and more
- Create different cards for different expenses for better expense management
- Assign reference codes and upload attachments for better expense management
- Get real-time updates on spending activity and know who’s spending what and where
- Streamline expense processes and automate reconciliation
- Capture more spend on your company card and earn more rewards
